Interpretation of PMVs:
  For frame pictures, 1st PMVs are for the top field,
      2nd PMVs are for the second field
  For field pictures, 1st PMV are for the upper 16x8,
      2nd PMVs are for the lower 16x8

Motion vector predictor updates:
  - forward and backward predictors are operated independently
  - for frame based prediction, the 1st PMVs are copied to 2nd PMVs,
    same for dual prime
  - for intra MBs or skipped P MBs, all PMVs are set to 0

